	<element name="Crystal Eye" type="Item" source="Drachenmurxer" id="ID_DRACHENMURXER_CRYSTAL_EYE">
		<description>
			<p>A cut crystal eye, translucent, with blue iris.</p>
			<p>The emblem of Vanyr, an open book in front of a sun, can be seen in it (spellcasting focus for Clerics of Vanyr).</p>.
			<p>Can also be used for the Spell Clairvoyance.</p>
		</description>
		<setters>
			<set name="category">Drachenmurxer Item</set>
			<set name="cost" currency="gp">100</set>
			<set name="weight" lb="0">0 lbs.</set>
		</setters>
	</element>
	
	<element name="Diamonds" type="Item" source="Drachenmurxer" id="ID_DRACHENMURXER_DIAMONDS">
		<description>
			<p>Shiny, shiny diamonds! In fact, these diamonds are so shiny they can bring somebody back from the dead - provided they have died within the last minute.</p>
			<p>Can be used as material component for the spell Revivify (consumed by the spell).</p>
		</description>
		<setters>
			<set name="category">Drachenmurxer Item</set>
			<set name="cost" currency="gp">300</set>
			<set name="weight" lb="0">0 lbs.</set>
			<set name="stackable">true</set>
			<set name="valuable">true</set>
		</setters>
	</element>
	
