	<element name="Small Knife" type="Item" source="Drachenmurxer" id="ID_DRACHENMURXER_SMALLKNIFE">
		<description>
			<p>A small knife urchins like to keep concealed in their clothes. One can never be too careful after all!</p>
			<p>Unarmed combat(Str/Dex) with advantage. </p>
		</description>
