	<element name="Sorcerer's Ring" type="Item" source="Drachenmurxer" id="ID_DRACHENMURXER_FYNNSRING">
		<description>
			<p>A slightly ostentatious ring that serves as a sorcerer spellcasting focus and doubles as  diamond component for the Chromatic Orb spell.</p>
		</description>
