	<element name="Trudust Flower" type="Item" source="Drachenmurxer" id="ID_DRACHENMURXER_TRUDUST">
		<description>
			<p>This creeping herb, which is often found on tropical trees, is prized for its potent medicinal properties. The red lance-shaped flowers are the only part of the plant used for medicinal purposes. The flowers can be used fresh or dried to make an infusion. 
			Dried flowers keep for about six months. If alcohol is added to the infusion, it can be stored for two years - Alchemy DC 20.</p>
			<p>Effect: A tea made from 3 flowers restores 2W6+2 HP</p>
		</description>
		<setters>
			<set name="category">Drachenmurxer Item</set>
			<set name="cost" currency="gp">0</set>
			<set name="weight" lb="0">—</set>
			<set name="stackable">true</set>
		</setters>
	</element>
	
